goodFood.deliveryService.deliveryApi -> goodFood.deliveryService.deliveryDomain "Expose" "In-process"
goodFood.deliveryService.deliveryEventConsumer -> goodFood.messageBroker "Consumes delivery commands" "AMQP"
goodFood.deliveryService.deliveryEventConsumer -> goodFood.deliveryService.deliveryDomain "Consume delivery commands" "In-process"
