goodFood.sagaOrchestrator.sagaManager -> goodFood.messageBroker "Consumes order events and publishes orchestration commands" "AMQP"
goodFood.sagaOrchestrator.sagaManager -> goodFood.sagaOrchestrator.sagaRepo "Store state" "In-process"
goodFood.sagaOrchestrator.sagaRepo -> goodFood.sagaDb "Store saga state" "PostgreSQL"
